<br>
I caught the glint of something in the milky light of my Stein. A gold glint that made me halt... did someone leave a coin? Some armor?<br>
<br>
&quot;HALT IN THE NAME OF THE FREEPORT MILITIA!&quot; a militia guard bellowed as he leapt out of the shadows. I easily stuck magical glue to his feet and made him stop in his tracks.<br>
<br>
I crossed my arms and glowered at the guard. He was struggling against his boots, and growling at himself for not packing some kind of magic removal talisman.<br>
<br>
&quot;What do you want from me NOW, you pustule?&quot; I teased.<br>
<br>
&quot;There's a new bounty for your head, Wizard, payable by Sir Lucan himself...&quot; the guard growled.<br>
<br>
&quot;NEW bounty?&quot; I said. &quot;What NEW bounty? I haven't killed any MORE of your guards in the commonlands, they pose no challenge to me anymore. They haven't in a long time.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;It's that paladin... that paladin that you helped steal Sir Lucan's testament... Sir Lucan is promising a thousand pieces of platinum for you dead...&quot; The guard managed to get one of his feet out of his boots, and I cast the Clash of Tishan on him, stunning him to limpness.<br>
<br>
I rolled my eyes. Always those lousy militia ruining my meditations. I guess now I'll have to go to the Commonlands and teach Lucan a lesson by destroying his presence completely...  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub16.ezboard.com/fdruzzilro86846frm7.showMessage?topicID=20.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub16.ezboard.com/fdruzzilro86846frm7.showMessage?topicID=10.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub16.ezboard.com/fdruzzilro86846frm7.emailToFriend?topicID=16.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub16.ezboard.com/fdruzzilro86846frm7.threadControl?topicID=16.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub16.ezboard.com/fdruzzilro86846frm7.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=16.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub16.ezboard.com/fdruzzilro86846frm7.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=16.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub16.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="druzzilro86846generaldiscussion">General Discussion<option value="druzzilro86846frm10">IRL<option value="druzzilro86846frm8">Raids<option value="druzzilro86846marketplace">Market Place<option value="druzzilro86846questsinfoandhelp">Quests, Info and help<option value="druzzilro86846frm7">Role-Players and St